title: COAST TO COAST AM - NOVEMBER 2013
description: I love listening to Coast to Coast and hate downloading all of the files, for each month, individually.  I haven't had a chance, yet, to enjoy these.  So they're untested but, hey, there's not too much that gone south with MP3s - this is the complete month of November, 2013.  I added a show with Jim Sparks, which is not from November 2013.   It sounded interesting, and I haven't had a chance to listen to it yet.....   That's my story - bada boom, bada bing.  Enjoy.
